@startuml

!theme plain 

title MyReadings — OCPVirt deployment process flow

actor Developer
participant "GitOps Repo" as Git
participant "ArgoCD" as Argo
participant "OpenShift + OpenShift Virt" as OCP
participant "VMs" as VMs
participant "AAP" as AAP

Developer -> Git : push manifests
Git -> Argo : webhook / repo sync
Argo -> OCP : apply manifests
OCP -> VMs : create VMs (ansible-managed=true)
AAP -> OCP : dynamic inventory sync
AAP -> VMs : run configure-*.yml
@enduml
